Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,子宮痉挛高潮 白阪有以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教\N请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是第2次的拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是第2次了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第2次的拍摄.第1次是什么心情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋感比较多吧 是这样感觉的\N-原来如此 如果太紧张的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒办法很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,出道时有很享受吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有享受过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,印象深刻的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是3P吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,3P?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的初体验也是啊\N在感觉爽快之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,像是男生就会先射精
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,女生不也是会有吗?像是快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那种的不想体验看看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想体验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊，好像沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-那手指插进小穴有过吗?\N-手指插进小穴只有过1次...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只有1次?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,1次 对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个..是初体验时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后对方先射了，那之后就沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天若能做到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,包含心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也包含兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-请对鏡头说说你的決心吧\N-好的，因为上次没能高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这次，能很享受然后能高潮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这次，要用这种的來做爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,习慣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不习慣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道这个是什么吗? 要怎么样用的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...我不知道欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个?-这里有开关，打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是美顏器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 也是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是更厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...这个是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,知道要怎么用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?-像是幅度大小的开关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,突起物好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有突起物...的肉棒有看过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒跟那种人做过爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊，因人而异的\N有说那种很棒的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要试试看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也做做看这种的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做的话，手就不能动了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以这样做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有以身体有感觉的地方是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头和耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很年轻卻很了解\N自己的敏感带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个自己也有在自慰吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很敏感呢\N是不是翘起來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,翘起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要再加強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样振动的舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下面...怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下面的也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为玩具有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要慢慢玩弄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，然后放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是玩具也有感觉啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢舒服的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,內裤要脫掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,超漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自己用腳夾住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,确定夾住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服的只有阴蒂吗?小穴里面呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面也好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有沒用到的玩具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可以用用看?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,变得真敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插入吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说请給我的小穴肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请給我的小穴肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自己翘起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢大的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要插到小穴深处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,多说点啊，小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听不见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴撑开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有以的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,全部清楚地看见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴撑开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,手借我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玩具交給你自己咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自己玩弄下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个调整強弱\N然后自己弄弄看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部也要弄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想直接摸?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.19,0:24:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.03,0:25:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是叫你看着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是，好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.18,0:25:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.06,0:26:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.05,0:26:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有以，我想要全部含进去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.04,0:26:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法全含进來...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.18,0:26:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那含到一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一半嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手也摸着睪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.04,0:29:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有也舔舔这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.19,0:29:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,换舔另一支
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.03,0:29:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢哪支肉棒?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.17,0:29:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.04,0:29:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的比较好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.19,0:29:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,含着小穴想插入的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这根肉棒要插入小穴里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想要你插
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.06,0:31:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了的话请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.11,0:31:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插进來了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.06,0:32:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.06,0:33:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.06,0:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒真好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.19,0:34:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒真好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插到哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.17,0:35:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插到小穴深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.04,0:35:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴里沒能够
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能全部插进來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.18,0:35:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴能全部插入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.06,0:35:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自己弄着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.07,0:36:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,插着底了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.17,0:36:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插着底了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.14,0:37:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.05,0:38:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.05,0:38:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.06,0:38:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.20,0:39:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.17,0:39:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全部看到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.04,0:40:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.09,0:41:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,手撑在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴被看得好清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.04,0:41:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在摩擦着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.07,0:43:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了，不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.06,0:44:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了，可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.06,0:44:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.03,0:44:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.17,0:44:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.05,0:44:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.09,0:45:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有以，大人的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.06,0:45:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.03,0:45:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是很舒服，但真的最舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.17,0:45:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的舒服的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.04,0:45:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.05,0:46:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.05,0:46:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不用紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.06,0:46:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,手也好光滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.13,0:46:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,指甲也好溧亮
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.04,0:46:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有点咸，可以舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.16,0:47:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有被舔过手指吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.06,0:47:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呢，这是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.06,0:47:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.17,0:47:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,手指全伸进來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.18,0:47:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,含的很深哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.18,0:47:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟叔叔做爱感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.05,0:47:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.05,0:47:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要听话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.06,0:47:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,制服很让人受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.20,0:47:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.17,0:47:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.23,0:47:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.11,0:48:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.20,0:48:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有做过这样接吻吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.06,0:48:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没怎么这样做过
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.17,0:48:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要舔耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.18,0:48:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头也可以伸进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.19,0:48:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.05,0:49:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.05,0:49:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.23,0:49:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.04,0:49:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.18,0:49:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,腰再往前点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.18,0:49:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.19,0:49:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.19,0:49:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.06,0:50:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.04,0:50:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻后就经很湿嘛\N这么喜欢接吻啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.26,0:50:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.20,0:50:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.17,0:50:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.04,0:50:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.18,0:50:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,湿哒哒的啊，让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.19,0:51:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.20,0:51:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这么湿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.17,0:51:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明还没舔小穴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.18,0:51:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.19,0:51:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很棒啊，好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.04,0:51:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮的胸部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.03,0:52:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.17,0:52:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把胸罩脫掉把
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔我最喜欢这种制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.18,0:52:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,朐部这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.05,0:52:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.19,0:52:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.03,0:52:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这种地方痒吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.17,0:53:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.19,0:53:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.03,0:53:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿哒哒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.17,0:53:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真色的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.18,0:53:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的阴毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.18,0:53:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这么稀疏嘛，这里也要舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.04,0:54:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.19,0:54:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股转过來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱的屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.20,0:54:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股很有弹性嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.17,0:54:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴咕噜咕噜的啊\N有感觉到吗?湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.19,0:55:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.06,0:55:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.06,0:55:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡的女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.18,0:55:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下來点
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.18,0:55:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.19,0:55:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得叔叔我現在在看哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.06,0:55:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.06,0:55:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门?你知道肛门这个词啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.20,0:55:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那叔叔也要开始舔肛门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.17,0:55:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.05,0:55:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.05,0:55:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很痒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.05,0:55:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸进去好了，可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.13,0:56:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.04,0:56:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里舒服?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.04,0:56:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门那里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.18,0:56:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡呢，翘起來，对的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.19,0:56:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.19,0:56:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门 有点撑开了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.06,0:56:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再多玩弄看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.03,0:56:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.04,0:56:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.06,0:57:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门有感觉啊，真是变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.34,0:57:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.18,0:57:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要让叔叔我一直舔到什么时候啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.05,0:57:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是肛门舒服就够了吗?小穴呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.19,0:57:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想要被你舔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.05,0:57:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被我舔小穴的嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.15,0:57:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.06,0:57:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你好淫荡啊，把腿张开來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.19,0:57:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那要开始舔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.05,0:58:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.20,0:58:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.05,0:58:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.20,0:58:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.05,0:59:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,做出很淫荡的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.18,0:59:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松看着
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.05,0:59:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.05,0:59:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.19,0:59:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.04,0:59:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.05,1:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好多爱液
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.20,1:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.18,1:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.20,1:01:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西流出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.17,1:01:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有流出来很多东西哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.17,1:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让叔叔舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.18,1:01:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很咸哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.19,1:01:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是从这里流出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.19,1:01:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.05,1:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.05,1:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.05,1:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.19,1:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.06,1:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很色的味道吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.19,1:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,张开来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.04,1:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边把膝盖跪起來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.04,1:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,接着能帮叔叔我舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.19,1:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.04,1:03:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.05,1:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.05,1:03:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.19,1:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,吸乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.10,1:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也舔一舔这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.04,1:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.04,1:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?叔叔我的腋下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.04,1:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒 忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.04,1:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,变成这样了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.05,1:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么味道?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.05,1:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-爱液的味道\N-爱液啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.06,1:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爱液的味道?是什么味道啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.06,1:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很咸
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.06,1:04:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.03,1:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很兴奋哦，叔叔我全都要舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.04,1:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦，含到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.19,1:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.04,1:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.04,1:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.18,1:05:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,边看这里边口交
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.19,1:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.19,1:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.16,1:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.03,1:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.04,1:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢口交吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.14,1:06:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.19,1:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔我又想舔了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.03,1:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不放开肉棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.17,1:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也能舔舔叔叔我的小肛门吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.18,1:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,边抽送肉棒边舔
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.19,1:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.19,1:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.06,1:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那多舔舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.04,1:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.07,1:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.05,1:09:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.19,1:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸进來了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.19,1:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.20,1:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么味道?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.03,1:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.08,1:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.19,1:09:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.20,1:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很苦嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.04,1:10:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.18,1:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,插进來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.19,1:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,咕噜咕噜的啊，先躺下來把
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.03,1:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有听见吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.18,1:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.05,1:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.06,1:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要拔出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.06,1:11:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要插到深处哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.05,1:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.05,1:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌激烈吗?咕噜咕噜的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.19,1:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.19,1:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看肉棒抽插的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.20,1:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里插着肉棒啊，这样怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.17,1:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.10,1:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.04,1:13:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.04,1:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要再來吗?抱住我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.18,1:13:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能自己扭腰?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.03,1:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自己抽插看看
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.03,1:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.03,1:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.17,1:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,手抓在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.04,1:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你抽动
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.19,1:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,頂到了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.13,1:15:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.06,1:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再做?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.06,1:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.06,1:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还能?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.17,1:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.18,1:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.19,1:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.20,1:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要插到深处了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.18,1:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.19,1:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.20,1:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.05,1:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴真紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.18,1:17:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.20,1:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.19,1:17:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下來，对的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.19,1:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.04,1:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔腳吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.05,1:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.19,1:18:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.04,1:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔我要快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.18,1:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.05,1:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.05,1:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.19,1:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.20,1:18:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.10,1:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要射很多精液了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.07,1:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,射啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.11,1:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，好像会射很多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.05,1:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要在这可爱脸上射出很多精液哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.06,1:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.06,1:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.06,1:20:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,说请給我叔叔的精子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.09,1:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.04,1:20:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.13,1:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.06,1:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,先弄干净
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.04,1:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,又射出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.19,1:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吐在手上哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.07,1:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有说了要高潮了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.04,1:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事?什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.18,1:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,至今沒有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.18,1:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好像能再更舒服一些?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.19,1:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.06,1:23:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.06,1:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,准备了这些东西
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.06,1:23:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.07,1:23:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,知道这些是什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.04,1:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,电动阳具，电动按摩棒
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.04,1:23:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跳蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.18,1:23:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跳蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.18,1:23:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是要怎么用呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.13,1:23:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不论用哪个
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.04,1:24:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都要戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.04,1:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想來用用玩具了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.04,1:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.05,1:24:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先帮你戴上哦，手给我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.19,1:24:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,动不了了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.06,1:24:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.20,1:24:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,动不了的狀态
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.17,1:24:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來让你舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.17,1:24:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,动不了了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.18,1:24:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要趁机多摸点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.05,1:24:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.19,1:24:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.18,1:25:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,痒痒的?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.04,1:25:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是很痒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.05,1:25:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再多感觉下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.06,1:25:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.20,1:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.04,1:25:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样摸很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.05,1:25:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.05,1:25:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.20,1:26:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡啊，还不能摸这里哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.17,1:26:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只能摸外側哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.05,1:26:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子要多用些玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.06,1:26:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来让你高潮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.13,1:26:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样玩弄的话
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.06,1:26:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会说再多摸下的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.04,1:26:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,多让我舒服点的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.04,1:26:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要多玩弄点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.06,1:27:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从胸罩上也能感受到
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.11,1:27:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头是这里?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.06,1:27:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.03,1:27:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听听看
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.04,1:28:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.05,1:28:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,露出來
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.19,1:28:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.20,1:28:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.06,1:28:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.04,1:28:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.17,1:28:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说多玩弄下乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.04,1:28:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,多玩弄我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.12,1:28:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.05,1:28:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只有旁边啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.20,1:29:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.18,1:29:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.19,1:29:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,变硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.04,1:29:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有弄到吗?弄到哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.18,1:29:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.04,1:30:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.04,1:30:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头可以这样两边夾着吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.18,1:30:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.05,1:30:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.05,1:30:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.04,1:30:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，变得硬梆梆了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.19,1:31:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脫掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.13,1:31:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.06,1:31:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.05,1:31:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在弄到舒服的地方喊Stop
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.18,1:31:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.05,1:31:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.04,1:31:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真色情啊，能看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.20,1:32:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.14,1:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,变得不妙了?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.18,1:32:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.10,1:32:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要直接玩弄吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.05,1:33:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙 这个
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.20,1:33:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.18,1:33:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.19,1:33:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,转到后面来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.19,1:33:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.03,1:34:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再多玩弄下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.04,1:34:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也有哦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.19,1:34:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.05,1:34:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.05,1:34:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.20,1:35:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有感受到吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.04,1:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小肛门也要被玩弄哦
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.18,1:35:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全都都要玩弄到
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.05,1:35:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,全部哦
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.19,1:35:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.06,1:35:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.04,1:35:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真湿啊，有听到声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.04,1:35:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咕噜咕噜的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.04,1:35:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再让你更能发出咕噜咕噜的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.18,1:35:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边，看着这边说也让里面舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.05,1:36:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也让里面舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.19,1:36:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看要插入了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.20,1:36:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能插入吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.17,1:36:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.18,1:36:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.18,1:36:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能感觉到在振动
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.05,1:36:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.19,1:36:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來，把它固定着
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.20,1:36:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.06,1:36:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,里面变得怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.07,1:36:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,里面
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.04,1:36:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有好好插着吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.11,1:37:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.19,1:37:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.20,1:37:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.19,1:37:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,里面和外面都舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.19,1:37:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.06,1:37:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.04,1:38:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.06,1:38:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.03,1:38:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.17,1:38:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，还插着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.05,1:38:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,转过來这边
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.19,1:38:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,里面也舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.11,1:39:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也帮你玩弄下乳头吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.18,1:39:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.19,1:39:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.07,1:39:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.18,1:39:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,又快高潮了?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.20,1:40:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.07,1:40:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.18,1:40:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.18,1:40:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.05,1:40:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.13,1:40:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.12,1:41:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用玩具 感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.59,1:41:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.52,1:41:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了几次啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.00,1:41:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,欸，大概4次还是5次吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.20,1:41:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-哪个最舒服?\N-电动阳具吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.17,1:41:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-喜欢插进里面的啊? -嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.11,1:42:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好性感的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.18,1:42:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但跟脸一点也不匹配啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.05,1:42:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不匹配吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.05,1:42:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是脸明明很可爱\N但是穿着很色情的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.06,1:42:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.06,1:42:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.06,1:42:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个..很像是水泡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.03,1:42:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好难的词啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.04,1:43:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很像润滑液?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.04,1:43:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.04,1:43:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有用过吗?这么大量的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.05,1:43:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.05,1:43:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.05,1:43:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那在这里，用这润滑液变湿滑
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.05,1:43:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后來做爱，感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.06,1:43:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.06,1:43:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,期待吗?先摸摸看把
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.04,1:43:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.17,1:43:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿润了，已经很透明了\N然后再倒上这个
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.18,1:43:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会变得更透明哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.05,1:43:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要倒上去才行
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.04,1:44:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,倒下去的时候有很淫荡的声音呢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.18,1:44:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.05,1:44:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.19,1:44:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要摸了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.20,1:44:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,跟平常被摸的比较下
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.17,1:44:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样被摸的会有不一样的感觉?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.04,1:44:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.19,1:44:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再多摸下
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.06,1:45:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.06,1:45:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.04,1:45:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真色啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.20,1:45:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也让我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.04,1:45:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,变透明了，看到小穴沒关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.19,1:46:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以倒在屁股上吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.06,1:46:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,倒上來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.19,1:46:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.12,1:46:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股湿湿滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.19,1:46:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要多摸下
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.04,1:46:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么感觉?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.04,1:46:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.18,1:47:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里变透明了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.19,1:47:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.04,1:47:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.04,1:47:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.04,1:48:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.12,1:48:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.19,1:48:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來摸好了，这里
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.20,1:48:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摩擦吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.06,1:48:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.06,1:48:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服就好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.06,1:49:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.06,1:49:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,变热了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.07,1:50:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再弄更湿滑点好了，自己抱着腳
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.17,1:50:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.18,1:50:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,像泳池一样
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.19,1:50:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.04,1:50:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拉开好了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.18,1:50:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看得很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.20,1:51:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这量很棒吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.04,1:51:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.18,1:51:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.19,1:51:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.04,1:51:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面也要哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.19,1:52:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.20,1:52:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一起被玩弄很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.06,1:52:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.06,1:52:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.06,1:52:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.05,1:53:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.20,1:53:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑的很舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.04,1:53:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.17,1:53:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.18,1:53:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.20,1:54:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?被什么东西摩擦着?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.04,1:54:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.18,1:54:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道被什么东西摩擦着吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.05,1:54:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.18,1:54:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,像在SEⅩ啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.06,1:54:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摩擦?抱住我
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.04,1:54:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,本来摩擦身体就很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.19,1:55:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那再用湿滑的身体來摩擦我
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.04,1:55:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.17,1:55:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头和乳头摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.19,1:55:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在摩擦着啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.06,1:55:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒和小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.07,1:55:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.18,1:55:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.05,1:55:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下內裤
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.06,1:56:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.04,1:56:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.18,1:56:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑的很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.18,1:56:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边，一直看着哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.19,1:56:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔身体好了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.06,1:56:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.20,1:56:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舔身体啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.08,1:57:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.19,1:57:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也要，摩擦肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.19,1:57:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.20,1:57:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.17,1:57:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉到肉棒越來越硬吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.18,1:57:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,多摩擦下
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.19,1:57:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.19,1:57:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.20,1:57:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要再倒点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.06,1:58:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,被摩擦着?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.20,1:58:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.20,1:58:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也要摩擦乳头，对
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.19,1:58:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头很硬啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.04,1:59:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,夾住了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.19,1:59:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.20,1:59:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.04,1:59:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.19,1:59:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來含着，就那样子，对
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.20,2:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.04,2:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.12,2:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.20,2:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咕噜咕噜的啊，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.19,2:01:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,口交好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.19,2:01:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要加这个看看?含在嘴里
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.20,2:01:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.04,2:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了?就那样口交吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.19,2:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真湿滑
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.05,2:02:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,吐出来
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.19,2:02:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抽送着那个
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.20,2:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,自己倒在肉棒上
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.04,2:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经习慣了啊，润湑液
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.18,2:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,边舔前端边抽送
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.04,2:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，含着再激烈点
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.18,2:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,手也可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.19,2:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.20,2:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.04,2:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办?肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.04,2:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想要插进來
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.04,2:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那屁股转过來，翘高点
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.19,2:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先來摩擦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.20,2:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我插入吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.04,2:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.07,2:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快插进去了啊，这个
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.04,2:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,插进來
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.04,2:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己来插入肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.05,2:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.19,2:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.07,2:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被怎样抽插?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.04,2:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,用力点的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.18,2:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.19,2:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.06,2:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.06,2:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.06,2:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.18,2:07:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.04,2:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.17,2:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，你动动看
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.19,2:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插得很深哦
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.20,2:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以躺着哦
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.04,2:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.04,2:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.07,2:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对，自己插下舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.04,2:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,流了好多汗，怎么了?很热吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.05,2:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很热
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.05,2:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不会冷吧?变热了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.05,2:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,变热了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.09,2:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,手撑在前面来抽动，好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.07,2:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.04,2:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.04,2:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.18,2:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手可以撑在前面哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.19,2:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.06,2:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.05,2:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿滑滑的呢，給我看下胸部
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.07,2:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.04,2:14:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.07,2:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,手撑在后面
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.18,2:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.18,2:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看得好清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.19,2:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,腳张好开啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:44.04,2:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再插进去
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.19,2:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.06,2:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.10,2:16:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.20,2:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢深处啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.20,2:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.07,2:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.19,2:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.05,2:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.19,2:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:56.20,2:18:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.07,2:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我快忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.20,2:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看着吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.04,2:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.18,2:19:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.19,2:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:00.20,2:20:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看着射出的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:20:22.05,2:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.05,2:20:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸看精液
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.18,2:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,腋下沾了好多
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.19,2:21:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那是润滑液吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.06,2:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道欸
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.20,2:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然湿湿滑滑的，但怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.07,2:21:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像的还要舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.20,2:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服?很激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.17,2:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很激烈，超激烈
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.18,2:21:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:24.15,2:21:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不，喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.09,2:22:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有以
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.19,2:22:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看看两側
Dialogue: 0,2:22:45.06,2:22:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有几个人?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.06,2:22:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有3个人
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.06,2:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有以好像还不满足的样子
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.20,2:22:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有不满足啦
Dialogue: 0,2:22:58.04,2:23:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有不满足吗?抱歉啊，\N我还专门准备了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.18,2:23:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要让谁回去?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.04,2:23:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不用了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:05.05,2:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哪边的?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.05,2:23:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,足够，足够
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.05,2:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,足够?什么足够啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.05,2:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有3个人的话
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.05,2:23:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有3个人的话?太好了，那事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.19,2:23:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.06,2:23:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,3个人要多摸下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.20,2:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,腳张开
Dialogue: 0,2:23:40.15,2:23:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.05,2:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敏感的地方是哪里?说出來
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.19,2:23:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.06,2:23:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的呢?说出3个地方啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.06,2:23:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有3个人啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:56.06,2:23:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,2:24:00.20,2:24:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.07,2:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵?耳朵敏感啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.04,2:24:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那请两侧的人舔吧
Dialogue: 0,2:24:06.04,2:24:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?耳朵
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.04,2:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:24:31.20,2:24:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?乳头
Dialogue: 0,2:24:44.18,2:24:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:24:48.18,2:24:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.19,2:24:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,腳张开，真色啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.04,2:25:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.18,2:25:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.19,2:25:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头来
Dialogue: 0,2:25:31.19,2:25:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好色的表情
Dialogue: 0,2:25:34.06,2:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒含过3支肉棒吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.20,2:25:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有这样做过吗?沒有吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.20,2:25:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会有很大支的來哦
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.05,2:25:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也摸这里
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.18,2:25:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋了，好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.06,2:26:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再张开点
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.06,2:26:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂在哪边?指出來
Dialogue: 0,2:26:12.20,2:26:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被怎么摸?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:14.07,2:26:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.04,2:26:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你做做看啊，教我们摸法
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.18,2:26:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,像那样吗?用中指溫柔的?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.18,2:26:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,继续摸，对
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.19,2:26:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸吗?这样?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:47.20,2:26:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.11,2:26:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:55.04,2:26:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.05,2:27:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.18,2:27:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵还有乳头?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:05.19,2:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后阴蒂?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:26.04,2:27:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.05,2:27:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再帮你多摸下好了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.19,2:27:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,膝盖跪着
Dialogue: 0,2:27:45.19,2:27:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,2:27:49.20,2:27:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,2:27:54.20,2:27:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股也可以多摸下吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:56.04,2:27:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,摸呀
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.18,2:28:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:28:10.19,2:28:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以拉下來吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:16.19,2:28:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，看到小肛门了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.20,2:28:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真色啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.04,2:28:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不知道要插多深啊\N自己来插插看吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.18,2:28:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能插到哪里好啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.19,2:28:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒关系吗?插那么深
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.06,2:28:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:49.06,2:28:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.06,2:28:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个?这个沒问題?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:06.11,2:29:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,里面 感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.04,2:29:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.18,2:29:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来好多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.12,2:29:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比较好吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:28.20,2:29:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:41.04,2:29:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，脫下來，再翘高点
Dialogue: 0,2:29:47.18,2:29:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要插入比刚才还粗的手指了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:29:52.19,2:29:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 粗吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:56.19,2:29:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:00.20,2:30:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.20,2:30:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:30:14.18,2:30:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,內裤变得湿哒哒的了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.18,2:30:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看，喜欢被舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.18,2:30:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:30:25.05,2:30:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你指名1人啊，要谁舔好?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.19,2:30:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己选
Dialogue: 0,2:30:36.20,2:30:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.06,2:31:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:31:15.14,2:31:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.18,2:31:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看着脸
Dialogue: 0,2:31:27.05,2:31:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗? 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:31:45.20,2:31:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真湿啊
Dialogue: 0,2:31:49.20,2:31:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.20,2:32:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:32:22.20,2:32:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再來吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:23.04,2:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,2:32:33.18,2:32:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.04,2:32:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:33:06.18,2:33:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:43.08,2:33:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也舔下我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,2:33:51.19,2:33:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:52.06,2:33:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:34:05.04,2:34:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想要和你做爱了
Dialogue: 0,2:34:18.12,2:34:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很湿润呢
Dialogue: 0,2:34:24.19,2:34:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:34:30.20,2:34:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,直接抽送
Dialogue: 0,2:34:53.15,2:34:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:35:19.05,2:35:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想含着肉棒吗?那蹲下來吧
Dialogue: 0,2:35:22.05,2:35:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下去啊
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.19,2:35:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,膝盖跪着
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.20,2:35:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对，还有哦
Dialogue: 0,2:35:38.20,2:35:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再抽送肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:35:43.04,2:35:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:35:57.19,2:36:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，能含到深处吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:06.19,2:36:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:36:12.20,2:36:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也舔另一边的肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,2:36:17.04,2:36:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边继续抽送着
Dialogue: 0,2:36:28.05,2:36:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.19,2:36:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,流口水了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.20,2:36:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有1支來了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:36:53.04,2:36:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你脸旁边都是肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:36:58.18,2:37:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，有被这么多肉棒包围过吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:04.19,2:37:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:08.19,2:37:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头来
Dialogue: 0,2:37:16.20,2:37:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:37:20.20,2:37:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很好看呢
Dialogue: 0,2:37:22.07,2:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:37:23.04,2:37:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒有几支啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:26.04,2:37:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,3支
Dialogue: 0,2:37:28.04,2:37:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再告诉我下，3支
Dialogue: 0,2:37:31.05,2:37:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,边看着脸边舔哦
Dialogue: 0,2:37:43.06,2:37:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那照順序舔哦
Dialogue: 0,2:37:49.20,2:37:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,换这边来
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.06,2:38:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.05,2:38:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴里面
Dialogue: 0,2:38:49.19,2:38:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真色啊
Dialogue: 0,2:38:56.20,2:38:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边，真好看啊
Dialogue: 0,2:39:00.20,2:39:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌头 同时舔2支
Dialogue: 0,2:39:06.17,2:39:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能这样含进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:46.05,2:39:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再用肉棒包围吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:49.05,2:39:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在沙发上
Dialogue: 0,2:39:53.19,2:39:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,用肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:40:07.20,2:40:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有边抽送边做爱过吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:08.07,2:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,2:40:16.18,2:40:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,插入了?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:21.18,2:40:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,插着里面了?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:23.05,2:40:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,插着了
Dialogue: 0,2:40:25.05,2:40:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?这支肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:40:26.05,2:40:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:40:31.19,2:40:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,2:40:41.20,2:40:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.06,2:41:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自己扭腰动起来
Dialogue: 0,2:41:52.04,2:41:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:41:59.18,2:42:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢插到深处吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:02.05,2:42:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:42:03.05,2:42:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒 这样插得很深吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:09.19,2:42:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很长啊，让我來插啊
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.19,2:42:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下來，对，就这样子
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.20,2:42:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢哪边?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:23.07,2:42:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.04,2:42:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:42:42.19,2:42:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:06.05,2:43:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,起來吧，舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:13.19,2:43:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:43:33.07,2:43:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:53.19,2:43:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:57.20,2:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,3支轮流抽插啊
Dialogue: 0,2:44:00.07,2:44:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,换这边的
Dialogue: 0,2:44:05.04,2:44:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:06.04,2:44:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:44:22.19,2:44:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:31.20,2:44:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:44:36.20,2:44:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,回到最初那根吧
Dialogue: 0,2:44:45.05,2:44:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:46.05,2:44:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:45:04.13,2:45:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把头抬高，看着鏡头
Dialogue: 0,2:45:08.20,2:45:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在被几支肉棒抽插过了?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:10.04,2:45:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,3支
Dialogue: 0,2:45:11.04,2:45:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,3支?全插过了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:12.04,2:45:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.04,2:45:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:45:19.18,2:45:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:45:31.19,2:45:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去
Dialogue: 0,2:45:40.20,2:45:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:45:51.05,2:45:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:46:02.19,2:46:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:11.20,2:46:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:46:30.12,2:46:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘起來
Dialogue: 0,2:46:49.20,2:46:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续抽插啊
Dialogue: 0,2:46:54.18,2:46:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我累了，让我舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:46:58.18,2:47:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己 能动吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:03.18,2:47:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:47:04.05,2:47:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:05.05,2:47:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:47:07.06,2:47:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抽送着
Dialogue: 0,2:47:15.20,2:47:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢插到深处啊?都插到根部了
Dialogue: 0,2:47:20.20,2:47:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:47:32.05,2:47:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:47:44.19,2:47:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要再继续抽插哦
Dialogue: 0,2:47:55.20,2:47:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:02.18,2:48:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:48:17.19,2:48:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:22.06,2:48:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:48:30.21,2:48:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:48:35.18,2:48:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,过來这边
Dialogue: 0,2:48:42.18,2:48:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:48:43.05,2:48:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:49:13.05,2:49:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,换我插了
Dialogue: 0,2:49:23.19,2:49:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱住我，对
Dialogue: 0,2:49:33.20,2:49:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:49:48.05,2:49:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,脸上的汗水好多啊\N因为太舒服了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:12.04,2:50:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,骑在上面
Dialogue: 0,2:50:20.18,2:50:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会自己动啊
Dialogue: 0,2:50:24.19,2:50:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,相当喜欢啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:26.05,2:50:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很自然啊
Dialogue: 0,2:50:48.04,2:50:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,2:51:25.05,2:51:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:51:26.05,2:51:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:51:31.19,2:51:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:51:57.05,2:52:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:52:13.19,2:52:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了啊这小穴,沒被这样说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.20,2:52:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有被说很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:52:27.04,2:52:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:52:44.19,2:52:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,含着
Dialogue: 0,2:53:05.05,2:53:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上下同样被抽插着
Dialogue: 0,2:53:29.20,2:53:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下來
Dialogue: 0,2:53:39.18,2:53:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，4P做了之后 怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:46.19,2:53:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,难受吗?哪难受啊?
Dialogue: 0,2:53:50.06,2:53:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,2:53:51.06,2:53:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是高潮太多次了吧?\N因为脸上汗水很多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:54:14.05,2:54:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:54:28.20,2:54:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: 0,2:55:06.10,2:55:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服，射了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:55:17.05,2:55:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:56:18.17,2:56:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也快射了
Dialogue: 0,2:56:28.08,2:56:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快射了，可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:56:31.05,2:56:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,射了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:56:41.20,2:56:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:56:58.15,2:57:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:57:12.19,2:57:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有1支哦，舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:40.06,2:57:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:41.06,2:57:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:58:03.04,2:58:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一起高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,2:58:05.05,2:58:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:58:14.19,2:58:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:58:53.06,2:58:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,4p怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:58:57.07,2:59:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:59:00.07,2:59:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了几次?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:02.07,2:59:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,數不清了
Dialogue: 0,2:59:08.18,2:59:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,身体还在顫抖呢，沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:27.06,2:59:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有话想对这3个人说的吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:32.07,2:59:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常满足了